Package game.fieldObjects

Class KeyObject

java.lang.Object
game.fieldObjects.KeyObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
FieldObject
public class KeyObject extends Object implements FieldObject
Represents key in pacman. Keys are immortal and immovable.
Author:
Ondřej Vrána
